Task listing, organized by user story:

(5) User story 1: As a health conscious user, I want to be able to calculate the Macronutrients based on personal goals and current weight so that I know exactly what my target daily intake should be. 

Task 1: (3) MACRO CALCULATOR
Task 2: (1) UPDATE DAILY GOALS BASED ON MACRO CALCULATOR
Task 3: (1) PROGRESS PAGE WHERE DAYS ARE TRACKED AND DISPLAYED IN A CHART

Total for user story 1: 10 hours

----------

(5) User story 2: As a product tester, I need to be able to see that the search function works with most, if not all, searches.

Task 1: (5) WEB SCRAPING (reverse engineering Safeway's private API)

Total for user story 2: X hours

----------

(3) User story 3: As a user, I want to be able to select brands and add to my daily diet.

Task 1: (3) UI CLEANUP (Make sure results from search show up in UI for the user to select and add)

Total for user story 3: X hours

----------

(1) User story 4: As a user who already knows what they want to eat, I should be able to just enter my chosen food instead of searching for it. 

Total for user story 4: X hours

